    "overview": "Success Human Resource Centre's Attendance Tracking System had a security vulnerability allowing manipulation of URLs to access PDF documents containing personal data of approximately 30,000 individuals. The organisation failed to comply with Section 24 of the PDPA (Protection Obligation) due to defective code in the Print_attendance function and Identity Access Management features.",
