    "citation": null,
    "decision_date": null,
    "industry": "Security Systems",
    "overview": "In June 2022, Metropolis Security Systems Pte Ltd discovered that personal data of 250 individuals (including names, NRIC numbers, addresses, mobile numbers and bank account numbers) had been exposed online via an open port. The exposure occurred due to a public folder misconfiguration during routine maintenance in March 2018, revealing gaps in the organisation's data security and information management practices.",
