    "outcome": "Written Voluntary Undertaking accepted by the Personal Data Protection Commission. The organisation committed to implementing 10 remedial actions including centralised storage of sensitive documents, deletion of expired records, annual information classification reviews, vendor supervision improvements, access control reviews, internal and penetration testing, and ISO27001 implementation.",
