    "overview": "SpeeDoc's AWS S3 bucket was misconfigured, exposing the personal data of 12,652 individuals including names, phone numbers, email addresses, NRIC numbers, lab test results, and photos to public access. The organisation took immediate remedial action and cooperated with the PDPC investigation, leading to acceptance of a voluntary undertaking rather than formal enforcement action.",
