    "outcome": "Directions imposed in lieu of financial penalty requiring: (1) implementation of reasonable pre-launch security testing for new online systems; (2) development and implementation of a data retention policy; (3) scans of Clear/Surface Web and Dark Web to confirm no publication of affected data online; (4) written update to Commission within 60 days.",
