    "root_cause": "Two zero-day vulnerabilities in the File Transfer Appliance (FTA) developed by Accellion Pte Ltd were exploited by threat actors to gain unauthorised access to the FTA's MySQL database. The discovery and rectification of these vulnerabilities fell solely within the responsibility and control of the developer, as only Accellion had access to the proprietary source code.",
