    "decision_date": "12 November 2021",
    "industry": "Manufacturing of networking, connectivity and cable products",
    "overview": "Belden Singapore and Grass Valley Singapore Pte Ltd notified the PDPC of a data breach affecting 189 individuals' personal data after an unauthorised third party accessed Belden Group's servers in the USA between September and November 2020. The case examined whether the organisations complied with Singapore's Transfer Limitation Obligation when transferring employee personal data to their overseas parent company for processing.",
