    "overview": "Commeasure Pte Ltd suffered a data breach affecting 5,892,843 customer records when threat actors obtained an AWS access key that was embedded in a defunct Android application package publicly available on the Google Play Store. The organisation failed to implement reasonable security arrangements under section 24 of the PDPA by embedding the access key in code and failing to include the application in security reviews for nearly three years.",
