    "overview": "Webcada Pte Ltd's three database servers were subjected to a ransomware attack on 29 August 2020, affecting the personal data of 522,722 individuals including names, phone numbers, dates of birth, addresses and order histories. The attack exploited improperly configured IPMI access settings and the organisation's failure to include IPMI in its vulnerability scanning regime.",
