    "overview": "ST Logistics fell victim to a phishing attack that resulted in Emotet malware infecting 6 user laptops, potentially affecting up to 4,000 MINDEF and SAF personnel. The organisation failed to conduct periodic security reviews that would have detected unpatched anti-virus software and incomplete installation of endpoint protection software, resulting in a breach of its data protection obligations.",
