    "outcome": "All three organisations found in breach of sections 12 and 24 of the PDPA. Directed to develop and implement intra-group agreements or binding corporate rules within 90 days, review internal policies to align with group standards within 90 days, and inform the Commission of completion within one week. No financial penalty imposed due to voluntary notification, no evidence of data exfiltration or misuse, and financial hardship concerns.",
