    "overview": "A registered seller on Novelship's e-commerce platform gained unauthorised access to personal data of six other sellers by manipulating public URLs, exposing names, email addresses, shipping addresses, hashed passwords, and bank account information. The breach resulted from the organisation's failure to conduct adequate vulnerability scanning before launching the website, specifically failing to test for OWASP Top Ten vulnerabilities.",
