    "outcome": "The Deputy Commissioner for Personal Data Protection found the organisation in breach of the Protection Obligation under section 24 of the Personal Data Protection Act 2012 and directed payment of a financial penalty of S$4,000 within 30 days. No other directions were required as the organisation had implemented necessary remedial measures.",
