    "overview": "A security employee used mobile phone numbers of eight building visitors collected during visitor registration to contact them for personal purposes, including requesting return of visitor passes and sending Chinese New Year greetings. The organisation had failed to implement standard operating procedures or guidelines for the retrieval and use of visitors' personal data, enabling unauthorised access and use.",
