    "case_number": "DP-1907-B4352",
    "citation": null,
    "decision_date": null,
    "industry": "Insurance",
    "overview": "FWD Singapore disclosed personal data of 71 individuals by sending 42 payment advice letters containing names and identification numbers to incorrect recipients between June and July 2019. The disclosure resulted from a logic error introduced when the organisation attempted to fix an earlier system error in its payment advice letter generation system.",
