    "decision_date": "2 March 2020",
    "industry": "Property Management / Condominium Management",
    "overview": "A security supervisor at Marina Bay Residences unauthorisedly disclosed CCTV footage containing identifiable individuals to a resident via WhatsApp and the footage was subsequently posted on Facebook. The management corporation failed to implement data protection policies, appoint a Data Protection Officer, and establish written data protection clauses in contracts with service providers, creating conditions that enabled the breach.",
