    "outcome": "The Deputy Commissioner for Personal Data Protection found the Organisation in breach of the Protection Obligation under section 24 of the Personal Data Protection Act 2012 and issued a warning. No directions were required as the Organisation implemented corrective measures including replacing manual code review with automated tools (Crucible and SonarQube) and improving test scenarios before deployment.",
