    "outcome": "The Commissioner found the organisation in breach of section 24 of the PDPA for failing to put in place reasonable security arrangements. The organisation was directed to pay a financial penalty of $16,000 within 30 days, with interest accruing on any outstanding amount at the rate specified in the Rules of Court.",
