    "case_number": "DP-1705-B0766",
    "citation": "[2018] SGPDPC [7]",
    "decision_date": "30 April 2018",
    "industry": "Education",
    "overview": "An individual signed up for a free brochure for a specific programme but received numerous unsolicited marketing emails unrelated to the programme. The organisation failed to obtain valid consent for sending these marketing emails and took approximately one month to process the individual's unsubscribe requests, continuing to send emails after withdrawal requests were made.",
