    "case_number": "DP-1609-B0194",
    "citation": "[2017] SGPDPC 9",
    "decision_date": "20 June 2017",
    "industry": "Gift hamper and floral bouquet retail and delivery",
    "overview": "A production employee used order forms containing personal data of approximately 24 individuals as filler material in a gift hamper, resulting in unauthorised disclosure of names, addresses, telephone numbers, and in one case an NRIC number. The organisation failed to implement reasonable security arrangements despite having instructions and policies in place.",
